aim_downtownbattle
Created by Le M

This map was created in three days of work.
Into it, you can take place in a battle into a destructed city center.
The terrorists spawn in a warehouse, while the counter terrorists spawn behind the buildings. That's a battle arena. The only goal to reach is to kill the opposite team.
There're two hidden weapons in the map.

Have a good game !
